 Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 484 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40542,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/07\/04\/even-smallest-blessings\/","url_meta":{"origin":18059,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Gratitude: Allah asks about even the smallest blessings","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 4, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBy the One in whose hand is my soul, among the blessing you will be questioned about on the Day of Resurrection are the cool shade, fresh dates, and cold water.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2369 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19346,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/06\/17\/allah-shade-relief\/","url_meta":{"origin":18059,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Shade: Allah shades those who give relief","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 17, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever grants respite to someone in difficulty or relieves him, Allah will shade him on the Day of Resurrection when there is no shade but His.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1306 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2675,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/31\/good-character-heaviest-mizan\/","url_meta":{"origin":18059,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Akhlaq: Good character is heaviest on the Scale","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 31, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNothing is heavier upon the scale of a believer on the Day of Resurrection than his good character. Verily, Allah hates the vulgar and obscene.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2002 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u062f\u064e\u0651\u0631\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0627\u0621\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41294,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/29\/honor-suppress-rage\/","url_meta":{"origin":18059,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Anger: Honor in the Hereafter for suppressing rage","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 29, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adh ibn Anas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever suppresses his rage, even though he could unleash it, Allah will summon him on the Day of Resurrection before the heads of all creation to choose whichever maiden he wishes.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2021 Grade:\u00a0Hasan\u00a0(fair) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/18059","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=18059"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/18059\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=18059"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=18059"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=18059"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}